   Gamarano, Daniel de Souza and Dias, Victoria Carolina Pinheiro Lopes and
   de Miranda, Carlos Alberto Silva and Tavares, Paulo Henrique Campos
   Prado},
Title = {Students perception at design school of the state Minas Gerais
   University (ED-UEMG) regarding the change of headquarters from Pampulha
   College to praca da liberdade},
Journal = {REVISTA DE GESTAO E SECRETARIADO-GESEC},
Year = {2023},
Volume = {14},
Number = {6},
Pages = {10479-10495},
Abstract = {This article presents a study carried out with the academic community of
   the School of Design (ED) regarding the change of headquarters, from the
   Pampulha college to Praca da Liberdade, this being the fourth transfer
   throughout its history, occurred in 2020. The ED UEMG stands out in the
   national scenario for its professionals' quality and for being one of
   the most representative courses in Minas Gerais. To carry out this
   analysis, students and collaborators participated in an online
   questionnaire with the Google Docs tool. The questions were structured
   to promote exploratory research on the change of the headquarters. In
   general, the results show that the change is considered positive by the
   community. This analysis was carried out by the students enrolled in the
   discipline of Applied Statistics for Research in Design offered in 2018
   at the Post Graduation in Design Program (Master and PhD degree).},
